title: Mystery Mammoth Tusk
description:
Detective Guy Raz and Detective Mindy are back on the case! This time, they're tasked with solving an underwater mystery... why in the world is there a mammoth tusk at the bottom of the ocean?! Grab your snorkles and join Mindy and Guy Raz as they get to the bottom of this case (and the ocean!)
